            "body": "```\r\n# ~/.zshrc\r\nneovim_autocd() {\r\n    [[ $NVIM ]] && nvim --server $NVIM --remote-send \"<C-\\\\><C-N>:silent cd $PWD<CR>i\"\r\n}\r\nchpwd_functions+=( neovim_autocd )\r\n```\r\n\r\nThank you @ZyX-I!\r\n\r\nThis works perfectly for me and it doesn't need another script.\r\n\r\nThe `i` at the end is needed to enter back into terminal mode so your screen doesn't jump on you.\r\n\r\n",
